{"tid":1811104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［推到比立場/蘋果/議員睇到］強烈要求使用「共派」取代「建制」稱呼","createTime":"2020-01-04T11:39:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T17:17:55.000Z","uid":258731,"like":76,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"82236f25b08bb29c91894d012a62253ce616fcb7","tid":1811104,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:39:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JSeVNTV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJSeVNTV.jpg&h=6e0e135a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n強烈要求各位同路人，議員，媒體停止對共派人士使用「建制」稱呼<br />\n<br />\n你覺得所謂的<del>建制</del>人士是建立制度嗎？<br />\n事實不是，他們破壞了香港長久而來賴以成功的自由制度，人權的保障，完善的法治<br />\n<br />\n停止使用<del>建制</del>稱呼，去標籤化，拉攏更多香港人支持，由你我做起<br />\n<br />\n<del>建制</del>派議員 &gt;&gt; <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">共派</span></strong></span>議員<br />\n<br />\n<del>建制</del>派政黨 &gt;&gt; <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">共派</span></strong></span>政黨<br />\n<br />\n<del>建制</del>派報章 &gt;&gt; <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">共派</span></strong></span>報章"},{"pid":"93440099650beb762120f61bfae5dad5d4449c36","tid":1811104,"uid":258731,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:40:04.000Z","msg":"全新概念 民主統戰部（想試下搞影子政府嘅，入黎幫手推）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1764866\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1764866</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f581bb3537c4dbe34eb927d82b0a46914cefd74d","tid":1811104,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:42:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9f822c110cdc647eed2273b9873e837fa19b61da","tid":1811104,"uid":36058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:45:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd030b96b3997cc91e3cdc497205aad54e70775","tid":1811104,"uid":12181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy